org.jasig.cas.support.saml.services.idp.metadata

Class SamlRegisteredServiceServiceProviderMetadataFacade

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.support.saml.services.idp.metadata.SamlRegisteredServiceServiceProviderMetadataFacade

  • public final class SamlRegisteredServiceServiceProviderMetadataFacade
extends java.lang.Object
    This is SamlRegisteredServiceServiceProviderMetadataFacade that acts a fa√ßade between the SAML metadata resolved from a metadata resource and other outer layers in CAS that need access to the bits of that metadata. Once the metadata resolved for a service is adapted and parsed for a given entity id, callers will be able to peek into the various configuration elements of the metadata to handle further saml processing. A metadata adaptor is always linked to a saml service.
    Since:
    4.3.0
